1
00:01:28,920 --> 00:01:30,239
How's the investigation on the mole?

2
00:01:31,480 --> 00:01:33,079
Chen Lezhang was on duty yesterday.

3
00:01:34,560 --> 00:01:35,319
If it's true

4
00:01:35,480 --> 00:01:37,159
that he lured the Crown Prince to the cell,

5
00:01:37,760 --> 00:01:39,319
but he's also the one who caught him.

6
00:01:39,920 --> 00:01:40,879
This Chen Lezhang

7
00:01:41,040 --> 00:01:42,120
has been detained pending trial.

8
00:01:42,920 --> 00:01:44,120
If he's the mole,

9
00:01:44,519 --> 00:01:45,599
and he lured the Crown Prince there,

10
00:01:46,159 --> 00:01:47,439
then the Crown Prince is innocent.

11
00:01:48,359 --> 00:01:49,120
At that moment,

12
00:01:49,400 --> 00:01:51,439
the Crown Prince was alone in the cell.

13
00:01:51,920 --> 00:01:54,319
If it wasn't the Crown Prince who killed him,

14
00:01:55,120 --> 00:01:56,200
could the Left Chancellor

15
00:01:56,760 --> 00:01:58,599
have killed himself to frame the Prince?

16
00:01:59,519 --> 00:02:00,840
Anything is possible.

17
00:02:07,280 --> 00:02:08,199
Zhang Yuancang

18
00:02:08,879 --> 00:02:10,479
used his Imperial Inspectorate identity

19
00:02:10,960 --> 00:02:12,520
to smuggle gold into the capital.

20
00:02:14,159 --> 00:02:15,199
Whoever could pull that off

21
00:02:15,719 --> 00:02:17,960
must hold high rank in the Inspectorate.

22
00:02:18,639 --> 00:02:19,560
Aside from the Purple Robe,

23
00:02:20,439 --> 00:02:21,719
that only leaves the Golden Robe.

24
00:02:29,520 --> 00:02:30,520
Why are you all looking at me?

25
00:02:32,639 --> 00:02:33,400
It wasn't me!

26
00:02:34,960 --> 00:02:35,599
I'm thinking,

27
00:02:36,039 --> 00:02:37,199
besides you and Chen Lezhang,

28
00:02:37,319 --> 00:02:38,840
are there any other Purple or Golden Robes?

29
00:02:40,199 --> 00:02:41,560
Any progress on the identity tablet?

30
00:02:42,280 --> 00:02:43,159
We've checked everything.

31
00:02:43,639 --> 00:02:44,400
No leads.

32
00:02:49,840 --> 00:02:50,840
The enemy hides while we're exposed.

33
00:02:51,280 --> 00:02:52,199
Our only option now

34
00:02:52,560 --> 00:02:55,080
is to lure the snake out of its den.

35
00:02:57,520 --> 00:02:58,280
Speak plainly.

36
00:02:58,879 --> 00:02:59,840
A diversionary maneuver,

37
00:03:00,719 --> 00:03:01,719
a secret strike.

38
00:03:04,280 --> 00:03:06,080
That tells us nothing. Isn't this just...

39
00:03:06,479 --> 00:03:07,280
a jailbreak?

40
00:03:15,960 --> 00:03:16,960
The Crown Prince has escaped!

41
00:03:17,039 --> 00:03:17,680
Guards!

42
00:03:28,919 --> 00:03:30,439
Your Majesty, please save the Crown Prince!

43
00:03:32,080 --> 00:03:33,719
Tell me, how am I supposed to save him?

44
00:03:34,319 --> 00:03:36,400
His Majesty decreed execution in 3 days.

45
00:03:36,759 --> 00:03:38,120
And His Majesty has yet to awaken.

46
00:03:38,520 --> 00:03:39,960
I don't even have a chance to plead.

47
00:03:40,960 --> 00:03:41,759
Reporting to Your Majesty,

48
00:03:42,319 --> 00:03:43,039
I have confirmed

49
00:03:43,719 --> 00:03:44,840
that the Crown Prince was framed

50
00:03:45,080 --> 00:03:45,919
for the Left Chancellor's murder

51
00:03:46,759 --> 00:03:48,280
by a mole in the Imperial Inspectorate.

52
00:03:49,280 --> 00:03:51,039
Ning Chen, this is a grave matter.

53
00:03:51,280 --> 00:03:52,080
Do you have proof?

54
00:03:52,520 --> 00:03:53,800
The proof lies with the Crown Prince.

55
00:03:54,560 --> 00:03:55,919
The execution is in just one hour.

56
00:03:55,960 --> 00:03:57,039
What are you still doing here?

57
00:03:57,800 --> 00:03:58,280
Your Majesty,

58
00:03:59,319 --> 00:04:00,159
my words carry little weight.

59
00:04:01,120 --> 00:04:02,879
Blocked by the Imperial Inspectorate mole,

60
00:04:03,240 --> 00:04:04,360
I had to take a desperate risk.

61
00:04:04,800 --> 00:04:06,960
I secretly broke him out of prison.

62
00:04:07,840 --> 00:04:10,000
I beg Your Majesty to uphold justice,

63
00:04:10,199 --> 00:04:11,319
safeguard the royal bloodline,

64
00:04:11,680 --> 00:04:12,599
sweep out the traitors,

65
00:04:12,759 --> 00:04:14,000
and clear the Crown Prince's name.

66
00:04:14,800 --> 00:04:15,960
How dare you!

67
00:04:16,639 --> 00:04:17,839
Why should I trust you?

68
00:04:19,839 --> 00:04:21,600
I stake my own head on it.

69
00:04:22,240 --> 00:04:22,720
Your Majesty,

70
00:04:23,680 --> 00:04:24,560
delay will bring disaster.

71
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:27,240
Acting in such a way

72
00:04:27,720 --> 00:04:28,839
is just like you.

73
00:04:31,519 --> 00:04:32,680
I'll trust you one more time.

74
00:04:32,879 --> 00:04:33,519
There's no time to lose.

75
00:04:33,800 --> 00:04:35,360
Tell me where the Crown Prince is.

76
00:04:36,560 --> 00:04:37,399
The Left Chancellor's residence.

77
00:04:37,959 --> 00:04:38,879
Is the Crown Prince safe?

78
00:04:39,199 --> 00:04:40,120
I dared not draw attention.

79
00:04:40,639 --> 00:04:41,639
I acted alone.

80
00:04:42,639 --> 00:04:43,920
He's alone at the Left Chancellor's manor,

81
00:04:44,360 --> 00:04:45,079
safe for the moment.

82
00:04:46,639 --> 00:04:47,560
I will immediately

83
00:04:47,720 --> 00:04:49,360
secretly have him brought into the palace.

84
00:04:49,639 --> 00:04:50,720
Once His Majesty awakens,

85
00:04:51,120 --> 00:04:51,839
we will decide our next move.

86
00:04:54,040 --> 00:04:54,920
You are wise, Your Majesty.

87
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:56,160
Go, quickly!

88
00:04:56,279 --> 00:04:56,680
Right away.

89
00:05:52,240 --> 00:05:53,879
I've been waiting so long for you.

90
00:06:04,120 --> 00:06:05,120
It's you!

91
00:06:05,560 --> 00:06:06,800
You're the mole!

92
00:06:49,120 --> 00:06:50,079
Arrest Ning Chen!

93
00:06:56,639 --> 00:06:58,360
You've finally shown your true colors.

94
00:06:58,920 --> 00:07:00,079
If I'm not mistaken,

95
00:07:00,720 --> 00:07:02,680
your note said the Crown Prince was dead.

96
00:07:05,519 --> 00:07:06,439
Actually, I had no idea

97
00:07:06,720 --> 00:07:07,959
who the real mastermind was.

98
00:07:08,639 --> 00:07:10,319
But if you'd actually gone to save him,

99
00:07:11,040 --> 00:07:12,639
that would've cleared your name.

100
00:07:13,600 --> 00:07:14,519
As it turns out,

101
00:07:15,560 --> 00:07:17,120
the Crown Prince really is innocent.

102
00:07:18,120 --> 00:07:19,079
I assume that by this very moment,

103
00:07:19,439 --> 00:07:21,600
the Imperial Inspectorate mole is caught.

104
00:07:23,079 --> 00:07:23,680
By the way,

105
00:07:24,959 --> 00:07:26,000
I really should thank you.

106
00:07:27,920 --> 00:07:29,439
Ning Chen, oh Ning Chen.

107
00:07:29,720 --> 00:07:31,120
Quite the clever scheme indeed.

108
00:07:31,879 --> 00:07:33,040
So what if you know?

109
00:07:33,920 --> 00:07:34,680
Are you aware

110
00:07:34,959 --> 00:07:36,519
that the moment you walked in,

111
00:07:36,759 --> 00:07:38,399
you were already a dead man?

112
00:07:38,959 --> 00:07:39,439
Take him down!

113
00:07:58,680 --> 00:07:59,160
Impressive.

114
00:08:02,680 --> 00:08:03,439
Just keeping it low-key.

115
00:08:27,079 --> 00:08:29,600
What a fine Empress you are.

116
00:08:30,319 --> 00:08:31,199
This poison...

117
00:08:31,879 --> 00:08:33,919
You'd even use it on me.

118
00:09:09,879 --> 00:09:11,000
Same old flavor.

119
00:09:12,399 --> 00:09:13,200
Delicious.

120
00:09:20,279 --> 00:09:21,399
So you believe

121
00:09:22,759 --> 00:09:25,480
the Crown Prince really did it?

122
00:09:25,919 --> 00:09:27,559
I merely raised one possibility.

123
00:09:29,279 --> 00:09:30,039
And then?

124
00:09:30,679 --> 00:09:32,639
He had a motive for the gold mine scheme,

125
00:09:33,039 --> 00:09:34,480
but no reason to collude with foreigners

126
00:09:34,759 --> 00:09:35,759
and betray his country.

127
00:09:38,879 --> 00:09:40,159
After saying all this,

128
00:09:41,000 --> 00:09:44,039
aren't you afraid I'll still trust him?

129
00:09:44,480 --> 00:09:45,039
After all,

130
00:09:45,759 --> 00:09:47,720
he is my own flesh and blood.

131
00:09:48,720 --> 00:09:49,440
Ning Chen,

132
00:09:50,080 --> 00:09:51,679
you wish to eliminate your rivals

133
00:09:51,960 --> 00:09:53,080
and seize absolute power.

134
00:09:54,360 --> 00:09:56,600
But that crown of yours

135
00:09:57,399 --> 00:09:58,919
isn't quite secure yet.

136
00:09:59,480 --> 00:10:00,759
Oh, my dear Your Majesty,

137
00:10:00,960 --> 00:10:01,919
I'm doing serious work here.

138
00:10:02,080 --> 00:10:03,440
Please stop teasing me.

139
00:10:06,000 --> 00:10:06,639
Go on.

140
00:10:09,399 --> 00:10:10,120
Since ancient times,

141
00:10:10,320 --> 00:10:11,240
struggles for the throne

142
00:10:11,600 --> 00:10:12,919
have always been fights over succession.

143
00:10:13,440 --> 00:10:14,799
Whoever stands to gain the most

144
00:10:15,039 --> 00:10:16,360
is the one behind it all.

145
00:10:17,279 --> 00:10:19,159
If it isn't the Crown Prince,

146
00:10:21,240 --> 00:10:23,039
who does Your Majesty think it could be?

147
00:10:25,279 --> 00:10:26,200
I have a plan

148
00:10:26,600 --> 00:10:28,200
that can kill three birds with one stone.

149
00:10:29,000 --> 00:10:29,960
However,

150
00:10:31,440 --> 00:10:33,240
it requires Uncle Tianxuan's cooperation.

151
00:10:44,120 --> 00:10:46,840
I believed I treated you well.

152
00:10:47,919 --> 00:10:49,279
Yet your methods

153
00:10:50,200 --> 00:10:52,879
are utterly devoid of conscience.

154
00:10:53,559 --> 00:10:55,080
I am the mother of this nation,

155
00:10:56,279 --> 00:10:57,480
the Empress of Great Xuan,

156
00:10:57,679 --> 00:10:59,440
your lawfully wedded wife.

157
00:11:01,159 --> 00:11:03,759
But when have you ever truly looked at me?

158
00:11:04,759 --> 00:11:06,120
What's wrong with my Zheng'er?

159
00:11:06,320 --> 00:11:09,120
You chose a maid's son as Crown Prince.

160
00:11:12,200 --> 00:11:13,879
Zheng'er is the legitimate heir.

161
00:11:14,399 --> 00:11:15,799
That it has come to this

162
00:11:16,200 --> 00:11:17,519
is all because of you.

163
00:11:18,279 --> 00:11:19,159
I have said before,

164
00:11:20,440 --> 00:11:22,679
the throne belongs to the worthy.

165
00:11:23,279 --> 00:11:24,759
But your heart is twisted.

166
00:11:25,759 --> 00:11:27,399
With a mother like you,

167
00:11:27,559 --> 00:11:28,679
what good could Zheng'er ever learn?

168
00:11:30,600 --> 00:11:31,840
You schemed endlessly,

169
00:11:32,600 --> 00:11:34,639
only to bring about your own ruin.

170
00:11:35,240 --> 00:11:36,120
If you show no mercy,

171
00:11:36,919 --> 00:11:38,279
then don't blame me for showing none.

172
00:11:39,600 --> 00:11:40,879
You think you've won?

173
00:11:41,519 --> 00:11:43,240
Right now, my Zheng'er

174
00:11:43,799 --> 00:11:46,279
has the Weilong Army besieging the palace.

175
00:11:46,879 --> 00:11:47,440
By now,

176
00:11:48,039 --> 00:11:49,519
they should be at the palace gates.

177
00:11:50,279 --> 00:11:52,000
Prepare to die.

178
00:12:01,879 --> 00:12:02,480
Zheng'er.

179
00:12:03,240 --> 00:12:03,759
Zheng'er.

180
00:12:04,679 --> 00:12:05,240
Zheng'er.

181
00:12:06,879 --> 00:12:07,320
Zheng'er!

182
00:12:07,360 --> 00:12:07,879
Mother.

183
00:12:09,080 --> 00:12:10,639
Mother, we've lost.

184
00:12:11,679 --> 00:12:13,159
They had set up an ambush long ago.

185
00:12:13,519 --> 00:12:15,159
The Weilong Army we built with such care

186
00:12:15,480 --> 00:12:16,279
is completely wiped out.

187
00:12:16,759 --> 00:12:17,720
How could this happen?

188
00:12:18,399 --> 00:12:19,399
Twenty thousand Weilong soldiers,

189
00:12:19,759 --> 00:12:21,120
crushed just like that?

190
00:12:23,559 --> 00:12:25,320
That is because His Majesty is wise.

191
00:12:25,600 --> 00:12:27,000
When the Left Chancellor was imprisoned,

192
00:12:27,200 --> 00:12:29,440
His Majesty foresaw your move.

193
00:12:29,960 --> 00:12:30,960
He had already ordered me

194
00:12:31,279 --> 00:12:33,960
to deploy Shenji Corps and 2,000 muskets,

195
00:12:34,120 --> 00:12:36,000
lying in wait for the right moment.

196
00:12:36,120 --> 00:12:36,840
All of this

197
00:12:37,440 --> 00:12:39,240
was within His Majesty's grasp.

198
00:12:39,480 --> 00:12:40,879
So he kept two thousand muskets

199
00:12:41,639 --> 00:12:42,879
for this very purpose.

200
00:12:44,399 --> 00:12:46,039
When did you begin to suspect me?

201
00:12:47,159 --> 00:12:49,399
The moment you and the Left Chancellor

202
00:12:50,279 --> 00:12:51,480
stole the gold mine, I already knew.

203
00:12:51,879 --> 00:12:52,639
What did you say?

204
00:12:54,240 --> 00:12:55,360
You knew all along?

205
00:12:56,360 --> 00:12:57,159
Eight years.

206
00:13:00,799 --> 00:13:01,840
Eight long years.

207
00:13:05,399 --> 00:13:06,320
Even when you

208
00:13:06,440 --> 00:13:09,120
had my beloved second son, Huai'en,

209
00:13:09,279 --> 00:13:10,399
poisoned to death,

210
00:13:10,559 --> 00:13:11,120
I

211
00:13:12,759 --> 00:13:14,279
still endured it.

212
00:13:21,799 --> 00:13:24,480
Waiting for the day you'd launch a coup,

213
00:13:24,639 --> 00:13:25,360
so I could catch you all

214
00:13:26,240 --> 00:13:27,480
in one fell swoop.

215
00:13:32,200 --> 00:13:33,840
How ruthless you are, Your Majesty.

216
00:13:34,879 --> 00:13:37,240
For Zheng'er, the Left Chancellor and I

217
00:13:37,320 --> 00:13:39,120
plotted countless schemes.

218
00:13:39,559 --> 00:13:41,200
That Your Majesty could endure it all...

219
00:13:42,200 --> 00:13:43,240
I have lost.

220
00:13:44,480 --> 00:13:47,120
I concede defeat.

221
00:13:48,440 --> 00:13:49,039
Father.

222
00:13:49,879 --> 00:13:51,679
Please spare Mother and me.

223
00:13:51,879 --> 00:13:53,200
M-mother and I swear,

224
00:13:53,360 --> 00:13:54,080
from this day on,

225
00:13:54,200 --> 00:13:56,679
we'll never set foot in the capital again.

226
00:13:58,080 --> 00:13:58,639
Get up.

227
00:13:59,799 --> 00:14:00,240
Mother.

228
00:14:00,440 --> 00:14:01,200
Don't beg him.

229
00:14:01,799 --> 00:14:02,960
He is so cold-hearted,

230
00:14:03,759 --> 00:14:04,639
how could he ever care

231
00:14:04,679 --> 00:14:06,399
for what little family bond we have left?

232
00:14:08,120 --> 00:14:08,559
Guards!

233
00:14:08,840 --> 00:14:09,320
Yes, Your Majesty!

234
00:14:09,919 --> 00:14:12,519
Take the Empress and Third Prince away,

235
00:14:15,440 --> 00:14:16,600
to be publicly beheaded at Meridian Gate.

236
00:14:17,879 --> 00:14:18,440
Come, Mother.

237
00:14:18,879 --> 00:14:19,399
Mother!

238
00:14:46,679 --> 00:14:47,559
Ning Chen.

239
00:14:48,960 --> 00:14:49,960
Come with me.

